        <p class="mb-3">Hover over the text below to see tooltips:</p>
        <div class="d-flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
            <p>
                This is a <partial name="Components/_ShahinTooltip" model='new {
                    Text = "helpful tooltip",
                    Tooltip = "This tooltip provides additional context and helpful information!",
                    Position = "top"
                }' /> example.
            </p>
            <p>
                Risk level: <partial name="Components/_ShahinTooltip" model='new {
